switch statements are an alternative to if statements. And in most cases has better potiential than if statements.
Switch statements spontaneously check to see if its assigned data matches on of its qualifications given, then
executes its programming. With this in mind it is capable of doing more than repeating the same line of code, and it is also
easier on the eye than a whole list of if statements. Switch statements are great for setting up gamemodes, or
navigating through pages for an example. It can check strings or integers.